      • printStackTraceInternally

        public static void printStackTraceInternally(java.lang.String message,
                                             java.lang.StackTraceElement[] stackTrace,
                                             int firstRow)
        ONLY MEANT BE BE USED IN THE info.collaboration-station.utilities PACKAGE. Prints a stack trace (starting from firstRow) which is preceded by a leading message ("\n" added to end of leading message) and followed by a newline at the end.
        Parameters:
        message - the message which appears just before the stack trace.
        stackTrace - The stack trace to be printed.
        firstRow - The first row of the stack trace, between zero and length.
